    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>Imp</abbr><ex>eratori</ex></expan> Cae<supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ari</ex></expan> divi Traiani Pa</supplied>rthici <lb n="2"/>filio divi N<supplied reason="lost">ervae nepoti Traian</supplied>o Hadria<lb break="no" n="3"/>no <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>usto</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>pontif</abbr><ex>ici</ex></expan> <supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>max</abbr><ex>imo</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>trib</abbr><ex>unicia</ex></expan></supplied> <expan><abbr>pot</abbr><ex>estate</ex></expan> IIII co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>uli</ex></expan> <supplied reason="lost">I</supplied>II res <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>ublica</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Tomita</abbr><ex>norum</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>aio</ex></expan> Ummidio Quadrato S<supplied reason="lost">allustio Serto</supplied>rio <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ato</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>usti</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>pr</abbr><ex>o</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>pr</abbr><ex>aetore</ex></expan> </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> Αὐτοκράτορι Καίσαρ<supplied reason="lost">ι θεοῦ Τραϊανοῦ</supplied> Παρθικοῦ υἱῷ θεοῦ <lb n="2"/>Νέρουα υἱωνῷ Τραϊανῷ <supplied reason="lost">Ἁδριανῷ Σεβαστῷ</supplied> ἀρχιερεῖ μεγίστῳ δη<lb break="no" n="3"/>μαρχικῆς ἐξουσίας <supplied reason="lost">τὸ δ ὑπάτῳ τὸ γ</supplied> βουλὴ δῆμος Τομειτῶν <lb n="4"/>Γ(άϊος) Οὐμμίδιος Κοδρᾶτος <supplied reason="lost">Σαλλούστιος Σε</supplied>ρτώριος πρεσβευτὴς τοῦ <lb n="5"/>Σεβαστοῦ <supplied reason="lost">καὶ ἀντιστράτ</supplied>ηγος καθιέρωσεν.
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Der Tafel besteht aus drei Fragmenten. Die oben angegebene Maße betreffen das linke Fragment. Die Maße der anderen zwei Fragmente (des rechten = CIL 03, 07539, des kleinen = CIL 03, 12493) sind unbekannt. (B): In Z. 4 bzw. 8 wird in den Textrekonstruktionen von AE 1977, IScM 2 und SEG 27 Quadrato S[evero? Serto]rio und Κοδρᾶτος [Σεουῆρος? Σε]ρτώριος wiedergegeben. In IGR 1 steht nur [? Arto]rio und [? A]ρτώριος AE 1985 korrigiert zu Quadrato S[allustio Serto]rio und Κοδρᾶτος [Σαλλούστιος Σε]ρτώριος.</p>
            </div>
